{{Use dmy dates|date=February 2016}} {{Use Indian English|date=February 2016}} {{Infobox person | name = Bidushi Dash Barde | image = | alt = | caption = | birth_name = Bidushi Dash | birth_date = {{Circa}} 1989 | birth_place = [[Orissa, India]] | death_date = October 2012 (aged 23) | death_place = [[Mumbai]], India | nationality = Indian | other_names = litchi, bd, bidu | known_for = good singer & dancer | occupation = actress, model | partner = Kedar Barde | years_active = 2008–2012 }}
'''Bidushi Dash Barde''' ({{Circa}} 1989 – October 2012) was an [[India]]n film actress and model based in [[Mumbai]]. She was second runner-up in the 2006 "Miss Chennai" beauty pageant. She had appeared in a few [[Tamil cinema|Tamil films]], including the 2006 crime-thriller ''[[Vettaiyaadu Vilaiyaadu]]''. The 23-year-old was found dead in her [[Andheri]] (West) apartment on 22 October 2012. Her death, caused by excessive bleeding, is the subject of a murder investigation.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/India-news/Mumbai/Former-beauty-queen-Bidushi-Dash-Barde-found-dead-in-Andheri-flat/Article1-949242.aspx|title=Former beauty queen, Bidushi Dash Barde, found dead in Andheri flat|publisher=Hindustan Times|date=2012-10-24|accessdate=2012-10-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026232131/http://www.hindustantimes.com/India-news/Mumbai/Former-beauty-queen-Bidushi-Dash-Barde-found-dead-in-Andheri-flat/Article1-949242.aspx|archivedate=26 October 2012|df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-10-25/chennai/34729074_1_kedar-barde-bidushi-dash-barde-shantanu-dash |title=Former city beauty queen found dead in Mumbai |publisher=The Times of India|date=2012-10-25|accessdate=2012-10-25}}</ref>
